name: Gemini Astrology
description:
Appropriately symbolized by the celestial twins. 
Because of Geminis' intrinsic duality, 
they're often falsely misrepresented as two-faced. 
In reality, however, Gemini rarely has a hidden agenda. 
Playful & intellectually curious, 
Gemini is constantly juggling a variety of 
passions, hobbies, careers, and friend groups. 
They are the social butterflies of the zodiac: 
These quick-witted twins 
can talk to anyone about anything.
